<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>인증 코드</title>
        <link
            rel="stylesheet"
            as="style"
            crossorigin
            href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/static/pretendard.min.css"
        />
    </head>
    <body
        style="
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #e8f0f0;
            font-family: 'Pretendard', 'Malgun Gothic', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        "
    >
        <div
            style="
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 800px;
                padding: 120px 70px 100px 70px;
                background: white;
                box-shadow: 0px 0px 30px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
                border-radius: 13px;
                box-sizing: border-box;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 100px;
            "
        >
            <div
                style="
                    width: 100%;
                    flex-direction: column;
                    justify-content: flex-start;
                    align-items: center;
                    gap: 30px;
                    display: flex;
                "
            >
                <div
                    style="
                        width: 100%;
                        text-align: center;
                        color: #333333;
                        font-size: 44px;
                        font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif;
                        font-weight: 700;
                        line-height: 1.4;
                        word-wrap: break-word;
                    "
                >
                    인증 코드
                </div>

                <div
                    style="
                        width: 100%;
                        height: 120px;
                        background: #ececec;
                        border-radius: 20px;
                        border: 1px solid #dedede;
                        display: flex;
                        justify-content: center;
                        align-items: center;
                    "
                >
                    <div
                        style="
                            text-align: center;
                            color: #2c3e50;
                            font-size: 50px;
                            font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif;
                            font-weight: 700;
                            line-height: 1;
                            word-wrap: break-word;
                        "
                    >
                        <%= verificationCode %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                style="
                    width: 100%;
                    flex-direction: column;
                    justify-content: flex-start;
                    align-items: flex-start;
                    gap: 30px;
                    display: flex;
                "
            >
                <div
                    style="
                        color: #333333;
                        font-size: 26px;
                        font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif;
                        font-weight: 500;
                        line-height: 1.4;
                        word-wrap: break-word;
                    "
                >
                    안녕하세요. 연암공과대학교 학우님,
                </div>
                <div
                    style="
                        color: #333333;
                        font-size: 26px;
                        font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif;
                        font-weight: 500;
                        line-height: 1.4;
                        word-wrap: break-word;
                    "
                >
                    회원가입을 완료하시려면 위의 코드를 입력해 인증을 완료해주세요.
                    <strong>(3분 후 만료)</strong>
                </div>
                <div
                    style="
                        color: #333333;
                        font-size: 26px;
                        font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif;
                        font-weight: 500;
                        line-height: 1.4;
                        word-wrap: break-word;
                    "
                >
                    감사합니다.<br />연암공과대학교 스터디그룹 매칭 플랫폼
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
